@261 = ~Conjure Animals~
@262 = ~Conjure Animals (Conjuration/Summoning)
Level: 6
Sphere: Summoning
Range: visual range of the caster
Duration: 4 turns
Casting Time: 9
Area of Effect: special
Saving Throw: none

This spell allows the caster to summon forth and control one or two Tshalas. These latters will replace the bears usually conjured by this spell, attracted by the aura of the preacher FireLord. If the conjuration requests it, they can cast spells such as "Curse", "Heal", "Feeblemind" and "Maze" once a day, as well as "FireBall" once per turn and at will. If they do not cast spells, they furiously attack any enemy of the preacher. They can hardly pay other services.~
