@2622 = ~Can cast again FireBall~

@264 = ~Animal Summoning III (Conjuration/Summoning)
Level: 6
Sphere: animal, summoning
Range: visual range of the caster
Duration: 4 turns
Casting Time: 7
Area of Effect: special
Saving Throw: none

By means of this spell, the caster calls one or two creatures that have 16 Hit Dice or less. Fire or having an affinity with fire creatures replace animals usually summoned by this spell, attracted by the preacher Firelord.
The summoned creatures aid the caster by whatever means they possess, staying until they are slain or the spell duration expires.~
