@265 = ~Aura of Flaming Death~
@266 = ~Aura of Flaming Death (Evocation)
Level: 6
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: 0
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 6
Area of Effect: 10-meters radius
Saving Throw: none

This spell causes the caster to be enveloped by an aura of intense flame that both injures opponents and protects from damage. This shield not only grants the user fire resistance and grants a 25% cold resistance. It also radiates in a wide area around the character.
For every round, an opponent within this radius suffers 1D4 fire damage points within less than 10 meters, +1D6 for creatures within less than 6.5 meters and +1D8 for all creatures within less than 3 meters radius (for a total of 1D4 + 1D6 + 1D8 damage points for creatures in the vicinity of the character).~

@267 = ~Detonate~
@268 = ~Detonate (Evocation)
Level: 6
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: visual range of the caster
Duration: instantaneous
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 3-meters radius
Saving Throw: special

A simple word and a gesture of the hand are enough to cast this spell, which creates a sudden explosion in the targeted area. The explosion is confined to a very small area in order to maximize impact, so much that in addition to dealing 1D6 +1 damage points per level of the preacher (smashing and fire, saving throw vs. spells to halve), the creatures hit are stunned for 1D4 for each round if they fail a saving throw vs. breath and are silenced for 1D6 per round if they fail the same saving throw with a -2 bonus.~
@2682 = ~Detonate (Evocation)
Level: 6
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: visual range of the caster
Duration: instantaneous
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 3-meters radius
Saving Throw: special

A simple word and a gesture of the hand are enough to cast this spell, which creates a sudden explosion in the targeted area. The explosion is confined to a very small area in order to maximize impact, so much that in addition to dealing 20D6 +20 damage points (smashing and fire, saving throw with a -2 bonus vs. spells to halve), the creatures hit are stunned for 1D4 for each round if they fail a saving throw vs. breath with a -2 bonus and are silenced for 1D6 per round if they fail the same saving throw with a -4 bonus.
All saving throws vs. this spell carry an additional -1 bonus every 5 level of the spellcaster beyond level 20.~

@269 = ~Exploding Mephits~
@2610 = ~Exploding Mephits (Conjuration/Summoning)
Level: 6
Sphere: charm, summoning, elemental (fire)
Range: visual range of the caster
Duration: 3 turns
Casting Time: 8
Area of Effect: special
Saving Throw: none

This spell acts in two rounds. First, it summons 1D4 +1 incendiary mephits subject to the sole will of the preacher. After which it loads them with explosive energy. Each Mephit thus transformed, when it dies, explodes into a FireBall inflicting 6D8 damage points (saving throw to halve) to all nearby creatures.~
