This spell can be used in two ways:
The Summoning of Exploding Mephits First summons 1D4 +1 incendiary mephits subjected to the sole will of the preacher. After which he loads them with explosive energy. Each Mephit thus transformed, when dying, explodes in a Fire Ball inflicting 6D8 damage points (saving throw vs. breath to halve) to all nearby creatures.
The Summoning of Quasit Kamizakes summons 1D4 +1 quasits subjected to the sole will of the preacher. After which he loads them with explosive energy. Each Quasit thus transformed will act as a kamizake will throw to the first enemy it will see to explode in a Fire Ball including the charge of its own energy, for a sum of 6D10 +12 damage points (saving throw vs. breath to halve) to all creatures in the area of explosion.~
