@2611 = ~Elemental FireBall~
@2612 = ~Elemental FireBall (Evocation)
Level: 6
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: 30 meters
Duration: instantaneous
Casting Time: 6
Area of Effect: 9-meters radius
Saving Throw: 1/2

This spell opens a portal on the elemental plane of fire, from where sprung a burst of magma that explodes into a FireBall that inflicts 1D8 damage points per level of the preacher (maximum 15D8). The victims who make a successful saving throw vs. spells will suffer only half damage.
This spell is especially useful against magic resistant creatures because they can't protect: the spell does not target them, it only summons a natural element.~
@26121 = ~Hellish FireBall~
@26122 = ~Hellish FireBall (Evocation)
Level: 6
Sphere: elemental (fire)
Range: 30 meters
Duration: instantaneous
Casting Time: 6
Area of Effect: 9-meters radius
Saving Throw: 1/2

This spell opens a portal on the plane of Gehenna, from where sprung a burst of magma that explodes into a FireBall that inflicts 15D8 damage points. The victims who make a successful saving throw vs. spells at -2 (additional -1 every 5 levels of the caster beyond level 20) will suffer only half damage.
This spell is especially useful against magic resistant creatures because they can't protect: the spell does not target them, it only summons a natural element.~
